<title>USA: RESEARCH ALERT - Ciber reduced.</title>
<headline>RESEARCH ALERT - Ciber reduced.</headline>
<text>
<p>-- Merrill Lynch said analyst Thatcher Thompson downgraded Ciber Inc to near-term accumulate from buy, and kept the long-term rating at buy.</p>
<p>-- shares opened off 1/2 to 34-1/2 on Monday.</p>
<p>-- company last week posted sharply higher third quarter pro forma earnings of $0.24 versus $0.13.</p>
<p>-- analyst not immediately available.</p>
</text>
